name: Fish map
author: tytkleva.net

sections.description:
Fisherman’s map plugin to quickly add a map to your site.

To be able to share the link, the js code is loaded, which changes the page anchor when the position of the map changes.

An example can be seen in the widget on the website https://tytkleva.net/
